                            <comment id="12769322" author="mikedd" created="Fri, 23 Oct 2009 18:41:58 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patches, BJ. The fix is in the latest SNAPSHOT builds. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
